        <title>Rust 每日学习 Day 5：引用与借用</title>
        <link>https://HHjoker.github.io/p/rust-%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0-day-5%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8E%E5%80%9F%E7%94%A8/</link>
