&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;The Rust Programming Language&lt;/a&gt;
